# CSS Colors

CSS provides multiple ways to add colors.

## Color Names

```css
h1 {
    color: red;
}
```

## HEX Colors

```css
h1 {
    color: #ff0000;
}
```

## RGB

```css
h1 {
    color: rgb(255, 0, 0);
}
```

## RGBA

```css
h1 {
    color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5);
}
```

## Background Color

```css
body {
    background-color: lightgray;
}
```

## Real-World Example

Brand colors improve consistency across websites.

Example:

- Amazon
- Facebook
- Netflix

Each uses unique color schemes.

## Summary

Colors improve visual appeal and branding.
